    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the tip. i'll try the whole grain thing. but i'm curious about the actual biology of it. like if the environment is right, why would the microbes just... not do their job? what are the actual microorganisms doing to make it rise, and how do they interact with each other in the dough?",
