      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay so it's basically a tiny ecosystem. i guess i'm just wondering if there's any way they can compete or if one side can accidentally take over and ruin the whole batch? like can the bacteria actually kill off the yeast or something?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
